reviewText: All these movies on blu-ray for a great price? This was a no brainer....

All of my favorite movies in one case.
Movie night was a blast
Every movie in this set was outstanding.  The outer case was broken, but the movies survived.
This is action personified.  Every movie is filled with adrenaline!

When opening the case .... The flaps inside the case that hold the Blu-ray discs were broken .... Disc were still held in place .... Disappointed .... I enjoyed 4 out of the 5 movies ... Good deal for the price ..... Main menus for each movie were not what I'm use to .... Something to get use to ... But wasn't really a problem ....
Unbelievable great set. Great presentation. Was gift for son. He loved it!
This box sets of movies is worth buying if you like these titles it would make a great gift for someone friend or family.
